summary: A small house in mixed Dwemer and Telvanni style.
descriptionHtml:
[size=2]A small house in mixed Dwemer and Telvanni style. Tel Mos is located near the Hillgrund's Tomb (On the way to Ivarstead). Look for map marker when you start game. [/size]

[url=https://www.patreon.com/haemprojects][left][size=2][img]http://tesall.ru/uploads/imgs/pre_1535556014__11111.png[/img][/size][size=5]﻿[b]Support Haem Projects on Patreon!
[/b][/size]
[/left][/url]
[center][img]http://tesall.ru/uploads/imgs/pre_1528135137__award.png[/img]﻿[/center]

[size=3][b]Features: [/b][/size]
[size=2]- Unusual design;
- All crafting stations;
- Common containers and bookshelves;
- Solstheim music in interiors;
- Fully navmeshed;
- Cleaned with Tes5edit.[/size]

[b][size=3]Requirements: [/size][/b]
[size=2]All DLC [/size]

[b][size=3]Uninstall: [/size][/b]
[size=2]Before uninstalling mod empty all containers and exit interior cell. [/size]
